        <h1>Dancing Tails</h1>
        <p class="centerText">
          Dancing Tails Dog Training is a local business that is located in the East Bay Area. My task was to create a website for the trainer.
        </p>
        <p class="center">
          <a class="button" href="http://dancingtailsdogtraining.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank" class="no-ajaxy">Web<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-new-window"></span></a>
        </p>
